# Configurable Dimensions - Test

Testing charts and maps with custom dimensions.

---

## Chart with Default Dimensions (800x600)

<<chart: bar>>
  data: [
    ["Q1", 120],
    ["Q2", 250],
    ["Q3", 180],
    ["Q4", 310]
  ]
  options:
    responsive: true
    plugins:
      title:
        display: true
        text: "Default Size (800x600)"
<</chart>>

---

## Chart with Custom Dimensions (1200x400)

<<chart: line width="1200" height="400">>
  data: [
    ["Jan", 45, 32],
    ["Feb", 52, 38],
    ["Mar", 61, 42],
    ["Apr", 58, 45],
    ["May", 67, 51],
    ["Jun", 75, 58]
  ]
  series: ["Sales", "Costs"]
  options:
    responsive: true
    plugins:
      title:
        display: true
        text: "Wide Chart (1200x400)"
<</chart>>

