## Square Chart (600x600)

<<chart: doughnut width="600" height="600">>
  data: [350, 280, 220, 150]
  labels: ["Product A", "Product B", "Product C", "Product D"]
  options:
    responsive: true
    plugins:
      title:
        display: true
        text: "Square Chart (600x600)"
<</chart>>

