## Extra Wide Chart (1600x500)

<<chart: bar width="1600" height="500">>
  data: [
    ["Jan", 120],
    ["Feb", 145],
    ["Mar", 168],
    ["Apr", 192],
    ["May", 215],
    ["Jun", 238],
    ["Jul", 265],
    ["Aug", 290],
    ["Sep", 312],
    ["Oct", 340],
    ["Nov", 365],
    ["Dec", 395]
  ]
  options:
    responsive: true
    indexAxis: x
    plugins:
      title:
        display: true
        text: "Extra Wide Chart (1600x500)"
    scales:
      y:
        beginAtZero: true
<</chart>>

---

# Conclusion

All custom dimensions must work correctly:
- Charts: 800x600 (default), 1200x400, 600x600, 1600x500
- Maps: 800x600 (default), 1400x700
